$ SQL*Plus: set pagesize
@ set pagesize

When using SQL*Plus to create SQL scripts or similar output, `pageset` should be set to `0` (and possibly
→ development/databases/Oracle/SQL-Plus/set/long[`long`] to large value).

sa:

  The default value of `pagesize` is changed when using SQL*Plus's `-fast` → development/databases/Oracle/SQL-Plus#sql-plus-start-options[command line option].

  → development/databases/Oracle/SQL-Plus
